    <item>
      <title>微软报告 Azure 云增长放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/microsoft-reports-slower-azure-cloud-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[微软股价在盘后交易中收复了大部分失地。该公司报告称，其 Azure 云部门增长放缓。这一结果加剧了投资者的担忧，他们急切地希望看到人工智能带来的回报。彭博社的 Ed Ludlow 对此进行了更多报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/microsoft-reports-slower-azure-cloud-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 05:28:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分析师称日本央行结果对日元影响喜忧参半，焦点目前转向美联储</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/boj-outcome-mixed-for-yen-focus-now-turns-to-fed-analysts-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师和策略师表示，日本央行加息并削减债券购买量后，日元大幅波动，因为会议结果并未真正明确央行的长期路径。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/boj-outcome-mixed-for-yen-focus-now-turns-to-fed-analysts-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 05:26:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元波动，日本央行加息、债券削减后日本国债维持下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/yen-drops-even-after-boj-lifts-policy-rate-as-yield-gaps-remain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受日本央行加息及宣布减少债券购买规模的影响，日元涨跌互现，债券价格维持跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/yen-drops-even-after-boj-lifts-policy-rate-as-yield-gaps-remain</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 04:12:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
